# Browserslist configuration for modern browsers only
# Eliminates unnecessary polyfills and reduces bundle size
# All these browsers support ES2022 features natively

# Modern Chrome, Edge, Safari, Firefox
> 0.5%
last 2 versions
not dead
not IE 11
not op_mini all

# Explicitly target browsers that support ES2022 features
Chrome >= 94
Edge >= 94
Safari >= 15.4
Firefox >= 93
iOS >= 15.4
Samsung >= 15

# Exclude older browsers that need polyfills
not Chrome < 94
not Edge < 94
not Safari < 15.4
not Firefox < 93
not iOS < 15.4
